{
  "stem": "13219.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was, at that time in 1939, I was 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A year after the bar mitvah, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Berezne shul.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a building, which its-- had a women's section upstairs and a man's a big hall with, with a nice altar with the, with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Torahs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a very, very famous rabbi by the name of Gedalche.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gedalche is G-E-D-A-L-C-H-E, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gedalche, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- very famous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never talk-- we never said the first name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Rabbi Gedalche.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I know that he came to Boston to raise money for a certain Jewish shul or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think he came down there in 1937 or '38.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians just-- they didn't have no opposition from the Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just-- because the Polish army had only cavalry, because-- and they didn't-- they didn't put up any fight.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember when this war started, they, they took my, my brother and my brother-in-law to the army, brother George.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the last thing we saw-- we know that after the war is over that he was in a prison in-- I mean, as a-- the Russians caught the whole army.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent them to Siberia, all of the Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poles mobilized--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An army.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took my brother and my brother-in-law as Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they, they had them somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the Russian army took him and took-- they didn't have too much fighting there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took him in prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They send him to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother was-- after they let him out from the prison camp, they, they gave him work in Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
